14:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'tkazma qiymati kalkulyatori komissiyalar va kurs farqini hisobga olgan holda pul o'tkazish yakuniy xarajatlarini hisoblaydi. Variantlarni solishtiradi: bank o'tkazmasi, pul o'tkazma tizimlari (Western Union, MoneyGram, Zolotaya Korona, Unistream), mobil o'tkazmalar (Uzum, Click, Payme). O'tkazmaning yakuniy qiymati = barcha komissiyalar yig'indisi + kursdagi yo'qotish."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekiston ichida o'tkazmalar uchun eng arzon usul — mobil ilovalar: Uzum — kartalar o'rtasida oyiga 10 mln so'mgacha bepul; Click — oyiga 5 mln gacha bepul; Payme — 3 mln gacha bepul. Turli banklar o'rtasida mobil ilovalar orqali o'tkazmalar — komissiya 0,3-1%. Hisoblar o'rtasida bank o'tkazmalari — 0,1-0,5%."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistondan xalqaro o'tkazmalar uchun: Zolotaya Korona — komissiya 1-1,5%, Rossiyaga o'tkazmalar uchun mashhur, naqd olish; Unistream — 1-2%; Western Union — 2-5% (qimmatroq, lekin 200+ mamlakatda mavjud); SWIFT — qat'iy -30 ( dan ortiq yirik summalar uchun foydali). Xalqaro o'tkazmalar uchun mobil hamyonlar: Uzum — Rossiyaga 1% dan."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'tkazma qiymatiga ta'sir etuvchi omillar: jo'natuvchi komissiyasi (0-3%), oluvchi komissiyasi (0-1%), kurs farqi (0,5-3% — kamroq foydali konvertatsiya kursi hisobiga yashirin komissiya), olish usuli (naqd kartaga qaraganda qimmatroq). Yirik summalarda qat'iy komissiya sababli SWIFT o'tkazma foydaliroq. Kichik muntazam o'tkazmalar uchun — mobil ilovalar."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Misol: Toshkentdan Moskvaga 5 000 000 so'm o'tkazma. Zolotaya Korona: komissiya 1,5% = 75 000 so'm. Western Union: 3% = 150 000 so'm. SWIFT:  ≈ 325 000 so'm (kichik summalar uchun foydasiz). Uzum o'tkazma: 1% = 50 000 so'm. Yirik summa ( 000) uchun: SWIFT  Zolotaya Koronadan () foydaliroq. Kalkulyatorimiz optimal usulni topadi."}]]}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Ko'p beriladigan savollar"}],["$","$L19",null,{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card px-4","children":[["$","$L1a","0",{"value":"faq-0","children":[["$","$L1b",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"O'zbekiston ichida eng arzon o'tkazma qanday?"}],["$","$L1c",null,{"children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"Mobil ilovalar: Uzum (oyiga 10 mln gacha bepul), Click (5 mln gacha), Payme (3 mln gacha)."}]}]]}],"$L1d","$L1e","$L1f","$L20"]}]]}],"$L21"]}]
